{"ID":"20260609124945-9wjzwxd","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260609124945-9wjzwxd","title":"2022年全国甲卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260609125032"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260609124959-ipjuur9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124959-ipjuur9","updated":"20260609124959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"能否将珍贵的文物置于掌中观赏品味？能否步入千年墓穴一探究竟？能否与未曾展出的国宝亲密接触？……与过去相比，今天的博物馆已经发生了①"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的变化。有了科技的助力，这些往日因时空限制而②"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的事情都已成为现实。“博物馆+高科技”让那些沉睡千年的古物“活”在了今人面前，为越来越多的人带来不一样的观展体验，让他们可以去那些原本“去不了”的地方，看那些本来“看不到的事物”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124959-t5cea9l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124959-t5cea9l","updated":"20260609124959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"故宫博物院举办的那场名为《清明上河图3.0》的高科技互动展演艺术，用现代超高清数字技术完美融合古代绘画艺术。"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"观众们沿着张择端的笔触走进繁华的北宋都城汴梁，穿梭于楼台之间，泛舟于汴河之上，观两岸人来人往，看水鸟掠过船篷。沉浸其中，确有一种③"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的情趣。在2016年的纪念殷墟妇好墓考古发掘四十周年特展上，首都博物馆利用虚拟技术带领观众“回到”妇好墓的考古发掘现场，上下6层、深达7.5米的妇好墓葬④"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。此外还有一些博物馆利用虚拟技术，以数字化方式展现文物全貌。观众只需在屏幕上滑动手指，就可近距离、全角度现赏文物，将静置于展柜中、封存进仓库里、消散在过往中的历史“托在手上”，全方位观察岁月留下的每一处细痕。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124945-z7gt6bx","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609124945-z7gt6bx","updated":"20260609125010"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260609125010-wmzpg5g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125010-wmzpg5g","updated":"20260609125010"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"17．请在文中横线处填入恰当的成语。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125010-91fkl08","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125010-91fkl08","updated":"20260609125010"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"18．文中画横线的句子有语病，请进行修改，使语言表达准确流畅。可少量增删词语，不得改变原意。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125010-i9g5q0r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125010-i9g5q0r","updated":"20260609125010"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"19．文中多处用了引号，下列四处引号中用法和其他三处不同的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609125010-4kymt6p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125010-4kymt6p","updated":"20260609125010"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．古物“活”在了今人面前"}]},{"ID":"20260609125010-l8gxvyp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125010-l8gxvyp","updated":"20260609125010"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．去那些原本“去不了”的地方"}]},{"ID":"20260609125010-f0j5kbq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125010-f0j5kbq","updated":"20260609125010"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．带领观众“回到”妇好墓的考古发掘现场"}]},{"ID":"20260609125010-xtcpcde","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125010-xtcpcde","updated":"20260609125010"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．将静置于展柜中、封存进仓库里、消散在过往中的历史“托在手上”"}]},{"ID":"20260609124945-nuegp2p","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609124945-nuegp2p","updated":"20260609125020"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260609124945-13600ci","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124945-13600ci","updated":"20260609125020"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"17．（1）翻天覆地（2）不可企及（3）身临其境（4）一览无余    18．故宫博物院举办的那场名为《清明上河图3.0》的高科技互动艺术展演，是现代超高清数字技术与古代绘画艺术的完美融合。    19．B"}]},{"ID":"20260609124945-jefxifs","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609124945-jefxifs","updated":"20260609125032"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260609125032-qy8r5pp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125032-qy8r5pp","updated":"20260609125032"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"17．本题考查学生正确使用成语的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125032-yho3gpd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125032-yho3gpd","updated":"20260609125032"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第一处，由“与过去相比，今天的博物馆已经发生了……的变化”“有了科技的助力，……都已成为现实”可知，此处是说博物馆发生的巨大变化，修饰“变化”，且要体现“变化巨大”，由此可以想到“翻天覆地”；“翻天覆地”，形容变化巨大。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125032-e7oqbjk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125032-e7oqbjk","updated":"20260609125032"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第二处，结合“些往日因时空限制而……的事情”可知，此处是说因时空限制而远到无法触及，由此可以想到“不可企及”；“不可企及”，没有希望达到，形容远远赶不上。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125032-qyl7mhd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125032-qyl7mhd","updated":"20260609125032"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第三处，结合“观众们沿着张择端的笔触走进繁华的北宋都城汴梁，穿梭于楼台之间，泛舟于汴河之上，观两岸人来人往，看水鸟掠过船篷。沉浸其中”可知，此处是说借助高科技，人们会产生如同亲身面临那种境地，由此可以想到“身临其境”等词语；“身临其境”，亲自到了那个地方。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125032-2d229yi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125032-2d229yi","updated":"20260609125032"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第四处，结合“首都博物馆利用虚拟技术带领观众‘回到’妇好墓的考古发掘现场，上下6层、深达7.5米的妇好墓葬……”可知，此处是说借助虚拟技术让妇好墓葬全部收入眼底，由此可以想到“一览无余”；“一览无余”，形容视野开阔或事物简单明了，一下就能全都看到。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125032-341ybtw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125032-341ybtw","updated":"20260609125032"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"18．本题考查学生辨析并修改病句的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125032-t5yawhx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125032-t5yawhx","updated":"20260609125032"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第一处，“举办……展演艺术”搭配不当，“举办”的不是“艺术”，而是“展演”，改为“举办……艺术展演”；"}]},{"ID":"20260609125032-chqxl01","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125032-chqxl01","updated":"20260609125032"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第二处，“用现代超高清数字技术完美融合古代绘画艺术”不合逻辑且语序不当，改为“是现代超高清数字技术与古代绘画艺术的完美融合”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125032-nlben66","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125032-nlben66","updated":"20260609125032"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"19．本题考查学生正确使用标点符号的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125032-q6g19vz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125032-q6g19vz","updated":"20260609125032"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．表特殊含义。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125032-hbquxw0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125032-hbquxw0","updated":"20260609125032"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．表突出强调。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125032-4t1mnkn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125032-4t1mnkn","updated":"20260609125032"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．表特殊含义。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125032-rdwq68w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125032-rdwq68w","updated":"20260609125032"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．表特殊含义。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125032-lb3ne9a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125032-lb3ne9a","updated":"20260609125032"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选B。"}]}]}